## The 7-11-4 Trust Threshold

For Conscious Founders to buy:
- **7 Hours**: Total exposure time with your content/brand
- **11 Touchpoints**: Distinct interactions across different times
- **4 Formats**: Video, text, audio, live (minimum)

### Implication for Farrice
Must create ecosystem of:
1. LinkedIn posts (text format)
2. Podcast guesting or audio (audio format)
3. Video testimonials or demos (video format)
4. Live conversations / calls (live format)

