| # | Trigger | Signal |
|---|---------|--------|
| 1 | **Time Bankruptcy** | "I've been meaning to post for 3+ months" |
| 2 | **Competitor Sting** | "Someone with less experience is getting all the visibility" |
| 3 | **Lost Deal** | "A prospect chose a competitor they found on LinkedIn" |
| 4 | **Failed DIY** | "I tried ChatGPT/Jasper — it sounds nothing like me" |
| 5 | **Team Pressure** | "My VP Sales is begging me to build my brand" |
| 6 | **Event Catalyst** | Funding round, product launch, speaking opportunity |
| 7 | **Peer Success** | "My friend hired a ghostwriter and his business exploded" |

